text.tspan: Based on the expert assessments and index by V-Dem, weighted by countries' populations. It captures to which extent
political leaders are elected under comprehensive voting rights in free and fair elections, and freedoms of association
and expression are guaranteed. It ranges from 0 to 1 (most democratic)
Data source: OWID based on V-Dem (v13); HYDE (2017); Gapminder (2022); UN (2022)
